      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Arts, Briefly report April 26 about HBO mini-series The Pacific; one of three marines to be featured, John Basilone, was killed on Iwo Jima in Feb 1945</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report in the ''Arts, Briefly'' column yesterday about ''The Pacific,'' a World War II mini-series that will be shown on HBO, referred incorrectly to one of the three marines the series will feature. John Basilone was killed on Iwo Jima in February 1945; he did not return home after V-J Day.</p>
      </block>
